snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 16 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
This is iPhone 16 Pro. Built for Apple Intelligence. A new powerful, private, personal, deeply integrated intelligence system to help you get things done effortlessly.

Powered by the new supercharged A18 Pro chip, with a faster Neural Engine, and an improved CPU and GPU. Which levels up both your iPhone and your gaming experience, offering our best-ever graphics performance.

Plus there‚Äôs an all-new camera system and an all-new way to control it. Use Camera Control to instantly access your camera, adjust settings, and take a photo.

And you can now shoot video in 4K 120 fps Dolby Vision to capture and edit stunningly cinematic slow motion.

Built with titanium. And featuring our thinnest borders for an even larger display.

iPhone 16 Pro is the most innovative, most powerful, and most intelligent iPhone ever. From the inside out.

Learn more about iPhone 16 Pro and iPhone 16 Pro Max: https://apple.co/4dSqFbR

localized.description:
This is iPhone 16 Pro. Built for Apple Intelligence. A new powerful, private, personal, deeply integrated intelligence system to help you get things done effortlessly.

Powered by the new supercharged A18 Pro chip, with a faster Neural Engine, and an improved CPU and GPU. Which levels up both your iPhone and your gaming experience, offering our best-ever graphics performance.

Plus there‚Äôs an all-new camera system and an all-new way to control it. Use Camera Control to instantly access your camera, adjust settings, and take a photo.

And you can now shoot video in 4K 120 fps Dolby Vision to capture and edit stunningly cinematic slow motion.

Built with titanium. And featuring our thinnest borders for an even larger display.

iPhone 16 Pro is the most innovative, most powerful, and most intelligent iPhone ever. From the inside out.

snippet.title: Rooh (Official Video) Amrita Virk | R Nait | Naiqra Kaur | Mad Mix | Punjabi Song 2024
snippet.description:
R Nait Music & Rajchet Sharma Presents "Rooh" by R Nait and Amrita Virk is a lively and heartwarming Punjabi track that blends traditional beats with a rich regional flavor. The song is set in a playful, conversational tone, making it feel like an engaging exchange between two people. It beautifully weaves themes of love, attachment, and the joy of being together, all while maintaining a lighthearted and fun atmosphere. The song‚Äôs breezy vibe and authentic musical elements capture the essence of a joyful connection.

With the PlayStation¬Æ5 Pro console, the world‚Äôs greatest game creators can enhance their games with incredible features like advanced ray tracing, super sharp image clarity for your 4K TV, and high frame rate gameplay.* That means you get to play PS5¬Æ games with the most impressive visuals ever possible on a PlayStation¬Æ console, and with 2TB of SSD storage included, your favorite games will be ready and waiting for you to jump right in for your next awesome adventure.**

PlayStation¬Æ Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) 
Get super sharp image clarity on your 4K TV using AI enhanced resolution for ultra-high definition play with astonishing detail.*

Kaffara Episode 44 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 9th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.

The film stars Vijay in dual roles, alongside Prashanth, Prabhu Deva, Mohan, Ajmal Ameer, Jayaram, Sneha, Laila, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Vaibhav, Yogi Babu, Premgi Amaren and Yugendran

Show Synopsis : Four brave female police officers of Aminabad police station use their wittiness and emotional intelligence to tackle the various challenges they face at their work. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution are mostly unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humour of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences which add to the drama and comedy.

Rapper Badshah joins us in the newsroom. In this exclusive interview, he addresses his long-standing feud with Yo Yo Honey Singh, responding to the allegations made against him. He also shares his journey from underground hip-hop to Bollywood stardom, discussing his controversial lyrics, his encounter with the mafia, and his relationships with big stars like Shah Rukh Khan and Salman Khan. He also discusses the story behind Mafia Mundeer. Don't miss this no-holds-barred conversation.

snippet.title: MAAHI VE || VREEGU KASHYAP || PRIYAM PALLABEE || APURAJ  || DHRITIMOY / ALAK  || ASSAMESE SONG 2024
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the enchanting world of love and emotions with our brand new romantic song, 'Mahi Ve'!

Vreegu Kashyap, the beloved voice of the Northeast, returns with another soulful masterpiece, continuing his annual tradition of gifting the people of Assam and beyond with heartfelt romantic numbers. With his velvety voice and unwavering dedication to his craft, Vreegu has become a household name in the region, and his music has transcended borders to touch the hearts of many.

Let the soulful melodies and heartfelt lyrics of 'Mahi Ve' transport you to a realm of passion and tenderness. Feel the warmth of love with every note, every beat, and every word. Get swept away by the captivating visuals and the chemistry of the lead pair.

In this video, YouTuber Bristi Gupta aka (Bristi Home Kitchen)  shares her inspiring journey of growing her YouTube channel from 300,000 to 1 million subscribers in just nine days during the lockdown. She recalls a shocking moment when her brother informed her that her channel was hacked, wiping out all her earnings.

 Bristi talks about her middle-class family, where her father ran a flour mill, and her mother was a homemaker. Initially lacking confidence to speak on camera, she decided to create cooking videos without her voice, using only music, and uploaded her first video on August 16, 2018. Despite personal challenges, including her father‚Äôs illness, she persevered and grew her channel to 1.2 million subscribers in just four months. 

Today, with over 5.3 million subscribers, Bristi uploads popular food and cake recipes on her channel, inspiring many. Her story demonstrates how a woman can work from home and inspire others, especially women striving to fulfill their dreams after marriage. Bristi is a role model for every woman seeking to turn her aspirations into reality.

Her Channel - @BristiHomeKitchen

In this video, YouTuber Bristi Gupta aka (Bristi Home Kitchen)  shares her inspiring journey of growing her YouTube channel from 300,000 to 1 million subscribers in just nine days during the lockdown. She recalls a shocking moment when her brother informed her that her channel was hacked, wiping out all her earnings.

 Bristi talks about her middle-class family, where her father ran a flour mill, and her mother was a homemaker. Initially lacking confidence to speak on camera, she decided to create cooking videos without her voice, using only music, and uploaded her first video on August 16, 2018. Despite personal challenges, including her father‚Äôs illness, she persevered and grew her channel to 1.2 million subscribers in just four months. 

Today, with over 5.3 million subscribers, Bristi uploads popular food and cake recipes on her channel, inspiring many. Her story demonstrates how a woman can work from home and inspire others, especially women striving to fulfill their dreams after marriage. Bristi is a role model for every woman seeking to turn her aspirations into reality.

Her Channel - @BristiHomeKitchen
